<body>
    <header class="header-sessions">
        <div class="header-logo-sessions">
            <a href="/users/new" style="text-decoration: none">
                <img src="/images/whitelogo.png">
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="header-buttons-sessions">
            <button class="button-activated">
               <a href="/users/new" style="color: white; text-decoration: none">메인</a>
            </button>
            <button>
                공지
            </button>
            <button>
                문의
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class ="header-login-sessions">
            <a href="login.html">
            <button>
                <a href="/sessions/new" style="text-decoration: none; color: white">로그인</a>
            </button>
            </a>
        </div>
        <div class="header-search-sessions">
            <button>
                <img src="/images/whitesearch.png" alt="search icon"/>
            </button>
        </div>
        <div class="header-instagram-sessions">
            <button>
                <img src="/images/instagram 2.png">
            </button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main class="login-main">
        <div class="main-login-sessions">
            <img src="/images/gympic11.png">
            <div style="white-space: nowrap;" class="main-login-left-sessions">
                <h1>
                    이제는 <br>
                    정착할 시간이에요.
                </h1>
                <div class="whiteline">
                </div>
                <h3>
                    헬스장, 필라테스, 그리고 요가까지 <br>
                    멀리 갈 필요는 없답니다.
                </h3>
            </div>
            <div class="main-login-right-sessions">
                <section>
                    <%= form_tag sessions_path do %>
                        <p>
                            아이디 <br>
                            <input type="text" name="name">
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            비밀번호 <br>
                            <input type="password" name="password">
                        </p>
                        <h4>
                            <input type="submit" value="로그인하기">
                            <div class="notice-sessions">
                                <%= flash[:alert] %><br>
                            </div>
                        </h4>
                    <% end %>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
